Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:12.35,0:00:15.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,[新機動戰記-鋼彈W]\NJust Wild Beat Communication
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:15.55,0:00:18.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,受到雨水拍打
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:19.02,0:00:22.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,決不褪色的熾熱思念
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:22.56,0:00:27.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,傳遍你的全身 TONIGHT!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:33.67,0:00:40.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,抱著你被淋濕的肩膀 想溫暖你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:40.88,0:00:48.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,顫抖的指尖 徬徨地在找甚麼?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:48.68,0:00:54.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我想留住你的視線
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:55.96,0:01:02.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,相信把悲傷變為力量的愛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:06.40,0:01:10.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,受到雨水拍打
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:10.07,0:01:13.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,決不褪色的熾熱思念
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:13.71,0:01:17.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,傳遍你的全身
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:17.41,0:01:19.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,TONIGHT!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:29.39,0:01:32.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,羅姆斐拉財團為了統治地球
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:32.43,0:01:35.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,以無人操縱MD為主要軍力
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:35.40,0:01:37.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,創立新生OZ
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:40.03,0:01:41.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,特列斯‧克修里那達
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:41.14,0:01:43.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,由於反對財團的功利主義
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:43.67,0:01:46.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他的所有權力被奪去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:46.24,0:01:48.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,組織形態出現改變
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:49.01,0:01:50.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但藉著MD的高性能
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:50.88,0:01:54.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他們決速地擴大了支配地域
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:55.52,0:01:57.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Ac195年
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:57.38,0:02:00.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,由於宇宙衛星認同了財團
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:00.25,0:02:01.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,財團下令殺死
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:01.52,0:02:05.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,完全孤立的鋼彈駕駛員
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:05.69,0:02:06.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,對他們來說
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:06.96,0:02:10.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,歷史的洪流繼續不斷倒流
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:18.21,0:02:19.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不要死
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:19.74,0:02:22.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,戰鬥，然後活下去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:22.64,0:02:27.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你，你們還不可以死
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:27.68,0:02:33.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,第三十四話\N[它的名字是次代]
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:47.67,0:02:49.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,到此為止嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:50.94,0:02:52.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,莉莉娜…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:05.75,0:03:07.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,特列斯派萬歲
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:37.69,0:03:40.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,特列斯大人…拜託你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:56.07,0:03:57.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,迪爾麥優侯爵
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:57.87,0:03:58.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,甚麼事?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:59.01,0:04:02.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,特列斯派全軍覆沒的\N消息來了嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:02.21,0:04:04.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不…那方面…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:04.68,0:04:05.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,為甚麼?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:05.91,0:04:07.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,投入那麼龐大的兵力
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:07.75,0:04:10.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他們為何還能支持下去?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:10.62,0:04:11.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,因為鋼彈
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:12.02,0:04:13.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,甚麼?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:13.22,0:04:15.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,鋼彈01出現了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:15.52,0:04:17.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,MD部隊也失去了半數
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:17.89,0:04:20.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,現在好像進入了混戰狀態
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:20.39,0:04:21.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這樣下去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:21.26,0:04:22.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我怕特列斯‧克修里那達
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:22.33,0:04:25.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,被帶走也只是時間的問題
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:25.63,0:04:28.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,怎麼辦?侯爵
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:28.10,0:04:30.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,通知未出動的所有地面部隊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:30.37,0:04:31.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,馬上前去盧森堡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:31.71,0:04:36.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,消滅特列斯派和鋼彈
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:36.14,0:04:37.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:39.65,0:04:44.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,特列斯始終只是迷惑士兵的虛像
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:44.15,0:04:48.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,和當作叛亂份子像徵的鋼彈一樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:48.69,0:04:53.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但是\N無論如何要阻止他們聯手
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:13.51,0:05:17.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,核對聲紋和指紋
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:17.22,0:05:19.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,請說出姓名
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:26.53,0:05:28.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,希洛‧唯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:28.73,0:05:33.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,資料核對確認，請入內
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:55.72,0:05:58.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你終於來了，希洛‧唯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:02.06,0:06:04.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我親愛的和平使者
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:04.53,0:06:06.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我衷心歡迎你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:06.47,0:06:07.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你就是特列斯嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:07.87,0:06:09.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不用懷疑
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:09.47,0:06:11.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,來，開槍殺我吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:11.94,0:06:14.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,為了結束戰鬥
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:19.91,0:06:23.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,做甚麼?只要我一日在世
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:23.28,0:06:25.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,戰鬥就不會結束
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:25.72,0:06:27.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你那樣想才來到這裡吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:27.89,0:06:30.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,告訴我讓我進來的原因
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:30.06,0:06:33.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那是數月前\N預先輸入電腦的關係
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:33.99,0:06:36.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我認為我終有一日
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:36.20,0:06:37.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,會和包括你在內的鋼彈駕駛員
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:37.47,0:06:40.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,盡情暢談一番呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:40.63,0:06:42.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我對你沒興趣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:42.77,0:06:43.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,當然
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:43.90,0:06:46.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你們只是想著和平就行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:47.01,0:06:48.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這個地球的…不
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:48.78,0:06:52.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,包括地球在內的\N整個宇宙的和平
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:53.78,0:06:56.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我只是想著戰鬥
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:56.08,0:06:59.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,和平只是戰鬥結束後的結果
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:59.85,0:07:03.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那麼，我問你\N你的敵人是誰?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:03.22,0:07:06.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我嗎?OZ嗎?羅姆斐拉財團嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:06.86,0:07:10.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,還是那些出賣了\N你們的遙遠故鄉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:10.56,0:07:11.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,衛星嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:11.87,0:07:15.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,站在我面前\N要取我性命的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:15.10,0:07:16.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那就是我的敵人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:16.97,0:07:19.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那種戰鬥沒結果啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:19.91,0:07:22.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,因為你的敵人就是命運
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:22.88,0:07:24.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,或許是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:24.21,0:07:25.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但我會戰鬥
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:25.95,0:07:27.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,只好繼續戰鬥
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:27.88,0:07:30.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,而且，何時死去也不在乎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:30.65,0:07:34.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你想享受自己的命運嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:34.29,0:07:35.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在那方面
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:35.49,0:07:40.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,莉莉娜‧匹斯克拉福特比你堅強啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:41.66,0:07:43.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我想不到你會在繼續戰鬥裡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:43.56,0:07:46.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,感到極限
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:46.07,0:07:47.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但事實上
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:47.33,0:07:50.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,無人能改變這個時代的演變
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:50.67,0:07:52.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你就能改變吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:52.94,0:07:55.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你以前掌握了歷史的主導權
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:55.84,0:07:58.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,再做一次同樣的事就行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:59.01,0:08:01.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我沒那心情
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:01.25,0:08:02.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:02.55,0:08:04.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,能和你暢談的現在
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:04.89,0:08:10.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是我人生裡最大的幸福
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:11.49,0:08:13.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,而且，我明白了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:13.89,0:08:17.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我和你一定要同生共死
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:17.23,0:08:21.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,互相賞識後，被神召見吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:21.10,0:08:23.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你這傢伙不輕易死心啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:23.90,0:08:26.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但我不在乎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:26.14,0:08:28.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不怕死的士兵嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:28.58,0:08:30.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我認為那姿態
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:30.11,0:08:33.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,才是正常人類正確的戰鬥方式
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:33.48,0:08:36.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但現在，你不知道誰是敵人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:37.02,0:08:39.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那方面和我一樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:39.52,0:08:42.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我的戰鬥也已經結束
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:42.29,0:08:44.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,根本未結束
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:44.89,0:08:48.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,為了你，許多士兵也正在死去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:49.00,0:08:53.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,至少，你的戰鬥未結束
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:55.20,0:08:56.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,如果結束了…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:56.84,0:08:58.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不，要結束的只是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:58.94,0:09:05.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我仍在繼續的悲痛\N而徒然的抵抗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:06.18,0:09:07.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,希洛‧唯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:07.45,0:09:12.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,請你不要再令我傷心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:12.22,0:09:16.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你不可以和我一樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:21.03,0:09:23.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這裡有指示你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:23.26,0:09:25.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,今後生存方式的路標
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:54.56,0:09:57.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這裡是稻草人五號\N發現飛翼O
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:57.43,0:09:59.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,現在開始工程
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:04.27,0:10:06.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,裝上這麼多，沒問題了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:06.27,0:10:08.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這是能炸毀三部里歐的份量
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:08.94,0:10:11.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好，返回里歐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:11.41,0:10:13.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,果然想炸毀它嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:13.95,0:10:16.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,當然吧，因為對OZ來說
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:16.22,0:10:18.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不，對羅姆斐拉來說
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:18.59,0:10:20.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,稱為鋼彈的東西
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:20.05,0:10:23.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是會成為支配的障礙的虛像
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:23.36,0:10:26.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,把真正的價值告訴他們吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:29.33,0:10:32.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好，現在炸毀飛翼O
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:32.87,0:10:34.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,發現物體高速接近
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:34.47,0:10:35.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,甚麼?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:37.20,0:10:40.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,托爾吉斯!閃電伯爵來了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:55.19,0:10:56.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可惡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:59.49,0:11:00.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這裡是稻草人五號
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:00.83,0:11:02.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,巴爾吉!托爾吉斯出現了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:08.17,0:11:09.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,為何逃避戰鬥?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:09.84,0:11:11.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,MD令戰士
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:11.61,0:11:14.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,連戰鬥方式也忘記了嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:14.41,0:11:19.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,還是\N我的思想已經落後了嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:19.81,0:11:21.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,小心，傑克斯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:21.08,0:11:24.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,MD的高速輸送船正接近
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:28.29,0:11:31.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,預知我會來而擺出的陣勢嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:34.23,0:11:36.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在倚賴MD的戰鬥上
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:36.93,0:11:39.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這是理所當然的戰術
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:53.15,0:11:54.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,MD的增援
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:54.72,0:11:56.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,準備很周詳啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:18.64,0:12:20.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,援軍嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:26.35,0:12:27.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,原來如此
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:27.75,0:12:30.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他們看來對我評價過高啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:31.22,0:12:34.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,7號機至12號機在後方散開
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:34.35,0:12:37.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你逃不掉的，閃電伯爵
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:53.11,0:12:54.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,托爾吉斯啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:54.51,0:12:57.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,全靠你，我才能戰鬥到現在
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:02.35,0:13:04.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我衷心感謝你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:10.32,0:13:12.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,和你告別令我傷心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:19.73,0:13:22.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但是，現在要戰鬥到底
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:31.78,0:13:34.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,永別了，托爾吉斯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:42.59,0:13:45.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我的愛機，安息吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:57.27,0:14:00.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,自爆了?他打算逃亡嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:00.47,0:14:02.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我會讓他那樣做嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:07.65,0:14:12.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是嗎? 他打算轉乘飛翼O吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:12.09,0:14:15.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,閃電伯爵看來也失策了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:18.66,0:14:21.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,指示MD更改目標…不
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:21.90,0:14:26.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,給他更匹配的死法吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:33.01,0:14:34.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在極樂世界咀咒吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:34.68,0:14:36.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你的天真決定
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:45.79,0:14:48.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這裡是稻草人五號，任務完成
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:48.52,0:14:51.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,消滅了飛翼O和托爾吉斯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:51.93,0:14:54.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,同時殺了傑克斯‧馬吉斯…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:03.30,0:15:06.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你們看來對飛翼O評價過低了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:26.66,0:15:29.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,非常好!這種反應速度
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:30.13,0:15:31.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這種戰鬥能力
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:49.08,0:15:51.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,身為完美戰士的你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:51.49,0:15:55.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不會被那部可怕的機體玩弄吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:56.22,0:15:59.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我祈求你選擇的路\N是正確的路啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:59.99,0:16:02.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,傑克斯，不，米利亞爾特
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:02.50,0:16:07.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你是通向和平的路標\N匹斯克拉福特
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:14.88,0:16:16.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,新型機嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:16.44,0:16:19.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我給它命名為[次代鋼彈]
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:19.18,0:16:21.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這部機體會讓駕駛員看見
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:21.92,0:16:26.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,敵人的模樣和駕駛員本身的未來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:26.09,0:16:29.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我根本沒有可以選擇的未來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:29.89,0:16:31.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,如果你駕駛這機體
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:31.56,0:16:34.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,和我有同一結果
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:34.29,0:16:36.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我們就一起跟這世界道別吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:36.90,0:16:39.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你為了甚麼造這種東西出來?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:39.77,0:16:41.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我認為繼續戰鬥
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:41.67,0:16:44.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是人類的存在意義
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:44.54,0:16:47.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但我不能從那裡找到答案
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:47.94,0:16:50.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,雖然我的戰鬥結束了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:50.21,0:16:52.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但我一定要從\N名為戰鬥的行動裡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:52.38,0:16:54.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,得到解答
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:54.08,0:16:56.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,作為達到那目的的機動戰士
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:56.12,0:16:59.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我認為鋼彈最有資格
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:59.72,0:17:04.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,而我想給予勝利者的戰敗者祝福
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:04.16,0:17:07.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這是令那心願\N有可能實現的機體
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:07.09,0:17:10.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你以為自己製造了神嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:10.30,0:17:11.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,或許
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:11.67,0:17:15.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,戰士有單純的戰鬥心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:15.74,0:17:18.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這部次代鋼彈就會有\N消除迷惘的機能
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:18.61,0:17:21.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不迷惘的戰士崇高而美麗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:21.51,0:17:22.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在某意思上
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:22.74,0:17:25.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,說得上最接近神的人吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:25.88,0:17:28.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我根本不信神
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:28.12,0:17:29.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,讓我看你的戰鬥吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:29.88,0:17:34.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,讓我看你的未來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:51.64,0:17:55.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,希洛‧唯，我先忠告你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:55.08,0:17:56.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,乘坐那機體後
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:56.51,0:17:58.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你不可以當勝利者
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:58.38,0:18:00.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,次代鋼彈也不是兵器
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:00.98,0:18:04.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,它希望你成為戰敗者回來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:04.08,0:18:06.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我也有那心願
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:06.22,0:18:09.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,希洛，在殺死我之前
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:09.42,0:18:11.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我不準你擅自尋死
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:11.43,0:18:13.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,因此，我解除了自爆裝置
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:35.88,0:18:38.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可惡!\N敵人的數目完全沒減少
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:38.95,0:18:42.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可惡的迪爾麥優不斷派增援來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:45.69,0:18:48.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,別放棄!戰鬥沒有結果
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:48.70,0:18:50.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,繼續戰鬥才有意義
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:51.50,0:18:54.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,六時方向發現物體高速接近
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:54.60,0:18:55.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,援軍嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:15.56,0:19:18.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那是…鋼彈嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:18.12,0:19:20.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是資料上沒記錄的機體
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:39.88,0:19:42.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,喂!那是…自己人嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:51.46,0:19:53.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,來了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:01.40,0:20:04.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我的敵人…不是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:04.07,0:20:06.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這些人只是被迫戰鬥…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:06.17,0:20:08.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好機會!攻擊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:09.84,0:20:12.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那麼…是這些人嗎…?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:12.25,0:20:14.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:20.62,0:20:24.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,一樣…這部機體和O一樣…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:32.00,0:20:34.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,把一切消滅
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:35.57,0:20:38.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,戰鬥的人全是敵人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:00.46,0:21:03.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,希洛，請你答應我…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:03.46,0:21:07.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,特列斯大人…拜託你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:12.47,0:21:17.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我根本沒有可以選擇的未來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:17.61,0:21:20.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我的…我的未來…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:20.31,0:21:22.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我的死亡…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:43.10,0:21:46.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,看見你的未來了嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:49.18,0:21:51.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:51.41,0:21:54.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那麼，開始吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:57.85,0:22:02.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,特列斯…我…沒那資格…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:13.43,0:22:16.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,待續
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:24.55,0:22:31.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,心血來潮的找人出來\N只因為天氣好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:32.55,0:22:38.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,讓我一直等不到人\N你以為你是誰
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:39.55,0:22:43.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我知道你是跑過來的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:43.55,0:22:46.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但那也是應該的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:47.05,0:22:53.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Just Love ! 那個惹人厭的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:54.55,0:23:01.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,捉弄人  是因為心理有愛意
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:02.05,0:23:09.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Just Love !  老是讓人掛念
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:10.55,0:23:17.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,對不起\N我不該說出強人所難的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:17.55,0:23:19.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,‧‧‧Just Love‧‧‧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:32.38,0:23:34.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,卡特爾為了和羅姆斐拉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:34.48,0:23:38.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,日益增加的壓力對抗\N他前去領取沙漠鋼彈
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:38.05,0:23:40.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,傑克斯希望和鋼彈駕駛員\N並肩作戰
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:41.02,0:23:44.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,遇上回到故鄉衛星的五飛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:44.29,0:23:46.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但再次被選為完成了的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:46.16,0:23:48.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,[雙龍鋼彈]駕駛員的五飛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:48.93,0:23:53.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,把傑克斯看作敵人，挑戰他
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:53.07,0:23:57.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,新機動戰記-鋼彈W，第三十五話\N五飛復出

